      <ul><br><br>
        <p class="MB_Heading">Skills: Monk</p>
        <ul>
          <p class="MB_SubHead">Weight restrictions, by level.</p>
          <ul>
            <p class="MB_Body"> 
              One of the restrictions of the monk class is that we lose Armor Class (AC) as our weight increases.<p>Depending on the level of the monk, there is an amount of weight you can carry with no penalty, but once you exceed the 'limit' for your level you start to lose AC. The AC penalty increases as you get more and more over the 'limit' for your level, and the penalty per pound increases the higher the level you are.<p>Here is a list of the limits:<p><ul><p>Level 1-14:   <15 No Penalty<p>Level 15-29:  <16 No Penalty<p>Level 30-44:  <17 No Penalty<p>Level 45-50:  <18 No Penalty<p>Level 51-54:  <19 No Penalty<p>Level 55-59:  <21 No Penalty<p>Level 60:  <25 No Penalty.</p></ul>
          </ul>
        </ul>
        <p class="MB_Submit">If you would like to submit an article to the site, 
          or have any comments on existing content, then email <a href="mailto:guides@monkly-business.com">Bodi 
          Kibadachi</a>. 
      </ul>
